y to be very private in the public-facing internet, but if you want to interact with us, we do hope to make some friends!\r\n\r\nThat said, we'd like to set some expectations in case anyone wants to communicate with us outside of Cohost. We're eternally anxious, always tired, somehow never have time, prone to panic attacks, prone to taking days\u002Fweeks\u002Fmonths\u002Fliteral years to get back to folks. It's not because we don't care. We really really _**really**_ care. But our brain is our brain and keeping up with the closest beings in our life is already taxing! We do want to try to reach out to others, and want to make connections \u003C3 Just don't expect continued communication please.\r\n\r\n\\\r\nMembers:\r\n\r\n@Zim-the-Vixen\r\n\r\n\\\r\nMental health issues has made it hard to get good at any thing, but will try to share art and origami!\r\n\r\n\\\r\nPlural; Therian, Non-Human, Not-People (most of us anyway!); Unrelentingly Queer and Trans, Polyamorous, Pan-Lesbian, Vegan, EN\u002FES, ADHD, Depression and Anxiety, Have a grave hyperFOXation, Probably-Other-Things!\r\n\r\nProud to have managed to block ourselves!\r\n\r\n\\\r\nAvatar by: Us~!","avatarURL":"https:\u002F\u002Fstaging.cohostcdn.org\u002Favatar\u002F81392-3c42b6b7-28d2-43a4-af77-28d9e2822ccb-profile.webp","avatarPreviewURL":"https:\u002F\u002Fstaging.cohostcdn.org\u002Favatar\u002F81392-3c42b6b7-28d2-43a4-af77-28d9e2822ccb-profile.webp","headerURL":"https:\u002F\u002Fstaging.cohostcdn.org\u002Fheader\u002F81392-bda91af9-6d69-4de4-82ca-10f01c37e377-profile.jpg","headerPreviewURL":"https:\u002F\u002Fstaging.cohostcdn.org\u002Fheader\u002F81392-bda91af9-6d69-4de4-82ca-10f01c37e377-profile.jpg","privacy":"public","url":"","pronouns":"they\u002Fit (plural) —Ask per heartmate","flags":[],"avatarShape":"circle","loggedOutPostVisibility":"none","frequentlyUsedTags":["Fluffies System"],"askSettings":{"enabled":true,"allowAnon":true,"requireLoggedInAnon":true},"contactCard":[{"service":"Discord! we'r